{"type": "article", "id": 11770, "title": "从250种标签到没标签，可口可乐想说的是同一件事", "description": "我们每一个人都和所有人一样特别。", "date": "2015-07-08T09:41:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12597, "name": "斋月"}, {"id": 330, "name": "可口可乐"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135455H5NfwTtVMBErmDUX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>中东伊斯兰教斋月期间，可口可乐推出一款限量版包装，首次使用没有可口可乐 </span><span>LOGO</span><span> 的包装来表示人人平等</span> <span>(Labels are for cans, not for people)</span><span>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span><span><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261358150U8t6iFpzNAHugcw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"425\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span></span><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><em>斋月：伊斯兰教规定为一年当中最圣洁的一月，在斋月期间穆斯林教徒从日出到日落期间戒斋、祈祷、阅读《古兰经》。</em></span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>该活动由麦肯环球迪拜子公司</span><span> FP7/DXB</span><span> 设计。可口可乐对此的解释是，“中东是一个有着 </span><span>200 </span><span>多个民族的地区，各种各样的标签让他们彼此分离，可口可乐去标签化的设计要传递一个强有力的、没有时间限制的讯息，即：没有标签的世界才是一个没有歧视的世界，我们都是一样的人。”</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span><span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135816bYnFu8pDV2sIy6H3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"425\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>有趣的是，去年可口可乐曾把人的名字放到包装上，推出了 </span><span>250 </span><span>款不同标签的可乐，提倡个性和分享的理念。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135455D7v5eQCWVtmGrN1f.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.99375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<span> \r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span><span>#ShareaCoke</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n</span> \r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>我们此前也<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/8422.html\">报道</a>过，</span><span>“Share a Coke”</span><span>作为一个全球范围内的营销活动，在包装上印制人名的创意最早诞生于</span><span> 2011 </span><span>年的澳大利亚。根据</span><span> Beverage Digest </span><span>的数据，</span><span>2014 </span><span>年可口可乐的销量实现了自</span><span> 2000 </span><span>年以来的首次增长。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>哦，还有昵称瓶、歌词瓶</span>……现在是无标签瓶，接下来该怎么办呢？\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}